body:
Hey, guys. 
I was encountered that problem recently. And I fix it just by put "fifo_queue_op.cc" in file 'tensorflow/core/kernels/BUILD'  inside the `filegroup(
    name = "android_core_ops", srcs = [ ...`, which configure the core kernel in Android.
